    <div style={{
      background: `linear-gradient(135deg, #0F1C3A 0%, #0B0F1A 60%)`,
      border: `1px solid ${C.border}`, borderRadius: 16,
      padding: "48px 40px", marginBottom: 32, position: "relative", overflow: "hidden",
    }}>
      <div style={{
        position: "absolute", top: -60, right: -60,
        width: 300, height: 300, borderRadius: "50%",
        background: "radial-gradient(circle, rgba(59,130,246,0.12) 0%, transparent 70%)",
        pointerEvents: "none",
      }} />
      <div style={{ color: C.accent, fontSize: 12, fontWeight: 700, letterSpacing: 2,
        textTransform: "uppercase", marginBottom: 12 }}>IRL Biomécanique</div>
      <h1 style={{ color: C.textPri, fontSize: 36, fontWeight: 900,
        lineHeight: 1.15, marginBottom: 16, maxWidth: 600 }}>
        Apprentissage par<br />
        <span style={{ color: C.accent }}>Renforcement Inverse</span><br />
        de la Marche Humaine
      </h1>
      <p style={{ color: C.textSec, fontSize: 15, maxWidth: 540, lineHeight: 1.7, marginBottom: 28 }}>
        Déduction de la fonction de récompense implicite optimisée par le corps humain lors de la marche,
        à partir de trajectoires biomécaniques observées sur 9 sujets sains.
      </p>
      <div style={{ display: "flex", gap: 12, flexWrap: "wrap" }}>
        {["MaxEnt IRL", "190 618 frames", "9 participants", "251 trajectoires"].map(t => (
          <span key={t} style={{
            background: "rgba(59,130,246,0.12)", border: `1px solid rgba(59,130,246,0.3)`,
